WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.444 --> 00:00:06.765
That is the glorification of God, 
 that is the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:00:06.765 --> 00:00:10.716
That's the encounter with living 
 God who is given to us but it is

00:00:10.716 --> 00:00:16.216
not given for us just to fill up with it 
 and enjoy, but to transform this world

00:00:16.216 --> 00:00:22.070
Today I will mostly focus on those secular 
 structures that this spiritual renewal needs to

00:00:22.070 --> 00:00:24.070
recover and renew.

00:00:28.368 --> 00:00:32.256
First, I would like to read a text to you. You saw a quote

00:00:32.707 --> 00:00:36.798
on our Facebook event that Marija put up 

00:00:36.798 --> 00:00:38.798
and I will explain why she put it.

00:00:38.798 --> 00:00:45.903
Jesus says in Matthew's gospel: "You are the 
 salt of the earth. But if the salt loses its saltiness,

00:00:45.903 --> 00:00:47.903
how can it be made salty again?

00:00:48.805 --> 00:00:55.807
You are the light  of the world. 
 A town built on a hill cannot be hidden."

00:00:58.404 --> 00:01:01.575
As we all know there is not 
 much salt. Salt is often invisible.

00:01:02.402 --> 00:01:04.459
Can anyone see salt in a soup?

00:01:04.459 --> 00:01:07.841
No one sees it. But try to imagine what 
 would that soup taste like without salt.

00:01:08.866 --> 00:01:11.399
It would be tasteless.

00:01:11.399 --> 00:01:16.392
When Jesus says this to Christians, He is 
 aware that there won't be that many real

00:01:16.392 --> 00:01:19.089
ones among them, but those 
 who are, need to give that spice.

00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:23.025
They need to bring Jesus's light 
 into the world right where they are.

00:01:23.804 --> 00:01:25.155
There's not much salt.

00:01:25.822 --> 00:01:30.835
Each one of you is sent right 
 where you are to bring Jesus's light

00:01:30.835 --> 00:01:35.951
and the more you are open to God, you 
 become a stronger weapon in His hands.

00:01:37.258 --> 00:01:40.820
A colleague of mine, a leader, says: 
 “You become like God's secret agent.”

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:43.106
That is true.

00:01:43.106 --> 00:01:48.772
You are inserted where you are to bring 
 Christ's light and to plunder souls from the devil.

00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:52.911
When he first told me this 
 I thought he might be exaggerating.

00:01:52.911 --> 00:01:57.142
Now that I live like that, I see that it is very much true.

00:01:57.142 --> 00:02:01.397
Each one of you is called to bring that difference.

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:06.701
Remember that simple image of 
 soup with and without salt.

00:02:06.701 --> 00:02:10.000
Jesus spoke in such a simple way 
 everybody could understand him.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:17.660
From Pharisees and literati to farmers and 
 husbandmen. His speech was simple but deep.

00:02:17.660 --> 00:02:21.833
That's how our acts should 
 look like: simple but deep.

00:02:25.153 --> 00:02:29.088
God entrusted our charismatic movement 
 the special grace and responsibility.

00:02:29.088 --> 00:02:33.703
In his addressing to charismatics on 
 the 50th anniversary, Pope Francis

00:02:33.703 --> 00:02:37.147
said that the charismatic movement is a 
 current of grace that needs to pour everywhere.

00:02:37.147 --> 00:02:40.591
That we must not stay where we are.

00:02:40.591 --> 00:02:46.240
That that current needs to pour on every 
 parish, every church, and the whole world.

00:02:46.740 --> 00:02:49.578
It seems to me that is where 
 the greatest problems begin.

00:02:49.578 --> 00:02:57.851
When we need to hand over the power, 
 consolation, and experience that we received,

00:02:58.794 --> 00:03:02.902
our comfort and regard are stopping us. 
 That's why the Pope has been calling us

00:03:02.902 --> 00:03:10.338
for years now, from the beginning of his 
 pontificate, to step out from sacristy.

00:03:10.795 --> 00:03:13.794
The Second Vatican Council and 
 previous popes have always been

00:03:13.794 --> 00:03:17.680
encouraging us Christians to 
 cure secular structures.

00:03:18.172 --> 00:03:20.000
We need to become aware

00:03:21.062 --> 00:03:24.415
that the power that has been 
 given, is given to us for renewal.

00:03:24.989 --> 00:03:26.989
Firstly, we are given the strength to repent 

00:03:28.219 --> 00:03:29.818
and to eliminate the sin.

00:03:30.188 --> 00:03:35.468
Considering that a life in sin hasspiritually 
 drained us, God gives that consolation.

00:03:35.714 --> 00:03:40.000
And that's why people who experience 
 God's mercy for the first time

00:03:41.175 --> 00:03:46.045
often cry and physically feel God's presence 
 even though they've never done that before.

00:03:46.414 --> 00:03:48.631
God renews man from the inside

00:03:48.631 --> 00:03:51.912
but he also gives him the power 
 to do something with that mercy.

00:03:53.797 --> 00:03:59.016
The problem is we often stop after receiving 
 mercy. I am often joking at our leaders' meeting

00:03:59.016 --> 00:04:02.348
when we criticize each other

00:04:03.250 --> 00:04:07.924
 that our charismatic movement 
 became charismatic stagnation

00:04:07.924 --> 00:04:11.400
or something similar to stagnation.

00:04:11.892 --> 00:04:13.241
It all stopped.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:18.093
God gave us that mercy to renew

00:04:18.749 --> 00:04:20.749
secular structures.

00:04:24.683 --> 00:04:30.000
Since God gave me the grace to travel through 
 Western and Eastern Europe a lot for the past

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:34.149
four years I would like to draw your 
 attention to these doings in Zagreb

00:04:34.149 --> 00:04:37.420
and the whole of Croatia. They are 
 a phenomena on the European level.

00:04:37.789 --> 00:04:43.898
I talked to a lot of priests, bishops, and leaders 
 that are frequently in contact with the Pope.

00:04:43.898 --> 00:04:45.898
This wakening of youth,

00:04:46.390 --> 00:04:50.000
where a great number of them 
 have the experience of the living God

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.031
and live sacramentally is unique in Europe

00:04:53.031 --> 00:04:54.908
and it is not happening anywhere else.

00:04:56.029 --> 00:05:00.779
Priests are in shock when they come here 
 from Western Europe and see full churches in

00:05:00.779 --> 00:05:06.156
Zagreb and lines in front of confessionals 
 even on Tuesdays, Wednesdays, and Thursdays.

00:05:07.235 --> 00:05:12.619
God wouldn't do such a thing accidentally 
 because He never did anything by accident.

00:05:13.316 --> 00:05:18.818
I would like to open your eyes so you 
 understand the moment that you're

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:23.545
living in because you are the 
 ones that need to carry this.

00:05:23.955 --> 00:05:25.868
There is a big problem

00:05:27.221 --> 00:05:30.656
when we do not recognize the moment of God's work.

00:05:32.656 --> 00:05:37.772
That happened in the Bible to courtiers 
 to whom the three wise men came first.

00:05:37.772 --> 00:05:41.994
The three wise men were watching the star. 
 They were astrologers and God enabled them

00:05:41.994 --> 00:05:46.782
to see that something big is happening 
 in the only way they would understand.

00:05:46.782 --> 00:05:49.783
They came to courtiers and 
 say: “Messiah was born!”

00:05:50.632 --> 00:05:53.580
and they answered: “That’s right. 
 That happened in that town because

00:05:53.580 --> 00:05:57.606
that's what the prophet said”, but they 
 themselves didn't go to Bethlehem to bow.

00:05:57.606 --> 00:06:04.010
While Jesus cries over Jerusalem in Luke 19:44 
 he says: “They will dash you to the ground, you

00:06:04.010 --> 00:06:06.010
and the children within your walls.

00:06:06.215 --> 00:06:10.454
They will not leave one stone on 
 another, because you did not recognize

00:06:10.454 --> 00:06:12.763
the time of God's coming to you.

00:06:13.460 --> 00:06:16.753
"Why did the ruin of Jerusalem happen?

00:06:16.753 --> 00:06:19.368
Because it did not recognize the time of God's visit.

00:06:19.614 --> 00:06:23.767
I’d like to inspire you. And thank God 
 I know that a lot of others will hear

00:06:23.767 --> 00:06:26.112
this through our YouTube channel.

00:06:26.645 --> 00:06:31.732
We must recognize that this is the time of 
 God's visit. God always visits with a purpose.

00:06:32.142 --> 00:06:35.577
Not just for us to renew and enjoy.

00:06:35.946 --> 00:06:42.753
It needs to become the power that is 
 given to renew and heal this world

00:06:42.753 --> 00:06:44.753
and coordinate it with the law of God.

00:06:46.265 --> 00:06:50.438
So Jesus says: “They will dash you to the 
 ground, you and the children within your walls.

00:06:50.438 --> 00:06:53.094
They will not leave one stone on another.”

00:06:53.094 --> 00:07:01.199
Jesus prophesied this during 
 the 33rd year after Christ.

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:04.317
That prophecy was fulfilled in 70. AD.

00:07:04.317 --> 00:07:11.778
That being said, it took thirty-seven years for it 
 to fulfil when Roman emperor Titus Vespasian

00:07:11.778 --> 00:07:13.778
completely flattened the whole Jerusalem.

00:07:15.213 --> 00:07:19.011
Why? "Because you did not recognize 
 the time of God's coming to you."

00:07:19.011 --> 00:07:21.011
There's always a risk

00:07:21.339 --> 00:07:24.733
that we won't recognize God's action

00:07:25.430 --> 00:07:29.275
because that's how we are. That's why I 
 encourage you to become the people of the Spirit.

00:07:29.275 --> 00:07:31.247
We all got problems with this.

00:07:31.247 --> 00:07:34.986
I often see that it's easy for us to 
 understand some Biblical messages through

00:07:34.986 --> 00:07:37.765
homily but it's hard to recognize 
 when it's happening to us.

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:43.956
Also, I often speak to the ones I follow 
 spiritually and say that the dryness will come,

00:07:43.956 --> 00:07:47.883
it will get harder and you'd want to give up if 
 you walk in faith but that's because God wants to

00:07:47.883 --> 00:07:49.883
bring you higher and deeper.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:52.837
When the dryness comes nobody remembers that.

00:07:52.837 --> 00:07:57.994
Everyone says: “God has left me, I should quit, 
 I'm fed up with everything, and this doesn't make sense.”

00:07:58.322 --> 00:08:03.542
We need to become the people 
of the Spirit, rise above our superficial 

00:08:03.542 --> 00:08:06.567
understandings, look around for what God does.

00:08:07.551 --> 00:08:11.125
The Holy Spirit is the one that gives us that. 
 People in the Old Testament could not do that.

00:08:11.125 --> 00:08:16.897
 That's why Isaiah says: “As the heavens are higher 
 than the earth, so are my ways higher than your

00:08:16.897 --> 00:08:19.242
ways and my thoughts than your thoughts.”

00:08:19.242 --> 00:08:26.356
But St. Paul says that: “we have the mind of Christ.” 
 speaking about a spiritual man in the New Testament.

00:08:26.356 --> 00:08:30.177
And trust me I know from personal experience. 
 I am not trying to sell you anything.

00:08:30.177 --> 00:08:32.382
I'm telling you about my experience that I am living.

00:08:32.915 --> 00:08:35.538
God has a need and desire to share

00:08:36.440 --> 00:08:37.547
with you

00:08:38.162 --> 00:08:42.335
 what he does in the world. 
 We just need to learn how to listen.

00:08:43.114 --> 00:08:45.114
And that's the art of prayer.

00:08:45.114 --> 00:08:49.017
We need to look at prayer as 
 a skill of warfare, spiritual warfare.

00:08:49.017 --> 00:08:54.256
We need to look at prayer as a skill of abidance 
 in God and a place to meet Him as a person.

00:08:54.256 --> 00:08:57.117
Then the prayer won't be just boredom. 
 In fact, we will be searching for some extra

00:08:57.117 --> 00:08:59.117
free time in our day for prayer.

00:09:05.126 --> 00:09:10.561
You are prophets by baptism. The Catechism of the 
 Catholic Church says clearly that everyone who has

00:09:10.561 --> 00:09:13.217
been baptized is a prophet, priest, and king.

00:09:13.217 --> 00:09:15.393
That's your identity and your destiny.

00:09:15.598 --> 00:09:17.902
Don't let anyone steal that from you.

00:09:19.810 --> 00:09:21.841
Do you know what prophet Amos says?

00:09:21.841 --> 00:09:27.794
"Surely the Lord God will do nothing, but 
 he revealed his secret unto his servants the prophets."

00:09:28.204 --> 00:09:30.189
God has a desire

00:09:30.763 --> 00:09:33.542
to share with us what's happening around us.

00:09:33.870 --> 00:09:35.641
Open your eyes and observe.

00:09:37.119 --> 00:09:40.000
Likewise, when He decided to destroy Sodom.

00:09:40.635 --> 00:09:46.600
The Book of Genesis says: “Then the Lord said, 
 "Shall I hide from Abraham what I am about to do?

00:09:47.945 --> 00:09:52.570
The parts of the Bible where God says 
 "Shall I" were always so interesting to me because

00:09:52.570 --> 00:09:57.481
we see in what way he thinks. We get to 
 know Christ's thoughts just as St. Paul says.

00:09:57.481 --> 00:10:01.449
The Bible says: "Why would I hide 
 from Abraham what I am about to do?"

00:10:03.114 --> 00:10:07.909
I’d like to open your eyes so you 
 acknowledge that this is the time of grace

00:10:07.909 --> 00:10:12.451
and we are obliged to get involved in it.

00:10:13.135 --> 00:10:20.625
Prophetically speaking, the Church did not teach 
 us all to take part in it and live as saints up

00:10:20.625 --> 00:10:23.089
until the 20th century.

00:10:24.015 --> 00:10:27.811
On the other hand, if you take a look at the saints 
 and movements that were rising in our Church

00:10:27.811 --> 00:10:29.237
throughout the 20th century,

00:10:29.237 --> 00:10:31.893
you'll see that they were mostly directed towards that.

00:10:31.893 --> 00:10:36.821
Look at Opus Dei for example. God lifts 
 Josemaria Escriva who says:

00:10:38.657 --> 00:10:42.297
“Housewives, husbands, wives, children,

00:10:42.748 --> 00:10:47.167
businessmen, politicians... They 
 all need to live a holy, supernatural life.”

00:10:48.804 --> 00:10:53.926
Cardinal Leo Suenens writes about the times 
 of the new Pentecost in Malines documents.

00:10:53.926 --> 00:10:56.164
What does the Bible say about the 
new Pentecost? It says: "And afterward,

00:10:56.164 --> 00:10:58.386
I will pour out my Spirit on all people."

00:10:58.755 --> 00:11:04.437
We need to become God’s prophetic people that 
 will listen to where God is sending them to

00:11:04.437 --> 00:11:05.863
act concretely.

00:11:07.790 --> 00:11:10.066
Also, it is necessary

00:11:11.009 --> 00:11:13.337
to use new methods.

00:11:13.583 --> 00:11:19.273
In his encyclical Evangelii Nuntiandi, Pope Paul VI 
 says that new evangelization needs to be

00:11:19.273 --> 00:11:21.396
new by methods and ardour.

00:11:21.396 --> 00:11:22.453
Why?

00:11:22.453 --> 00:11:25.765
You can’t approach the youth with 
 some kind of old story anymore.

00:11:27.601 --> 00:11:31.660
You and the whole Church always need to 
 protect the doctrine because the doctrine saved

00:11:31.660 --> 00:11:35.218
 the Church for two thousand 
 years and it is of divine origin,

00:11:35.218 --> 00:11:37.546
but the way it approaches people

00:11:37.792 --> 00:11:41.637
the speech, and the methods it uses need to be new.

00:11:42.088 --> 00:11:46.917
The ardour needs to be new and 
 that can be given only by the Holy Spirit.

00:11:46.917 --> 00:11:51.763
Cardinal Suenens encourages us to use 
 the knowledge and achievements of the world.

00:11:52.857 --> 00:11:56.288
 These are the documents we 
 will deal with throughout this year.

00:11:56.534 --> 00:12:02.364
That is the manifest of Catholic Charismatic 
 Renewal and our basic document.

00:12:02.989 --> 00:12:05.008
It is important for us to get to know it.

00:12:06.816 --> 00:12:12.724
Cardinal Suenens says: "A purifying critique can 
come within and without. Sometimes it even

00:12:12.724 --> 00:12:13.945
comes from our enemy.”

00:12:13.945 --> 00:12:17.789
The saying: “It is good to learn from 
 your enemies.” refers to the Church too.

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:24.176
The Church has a binding reason for 
 reconsideration on a human level because

00:12:24.176 --> 00:12:26.176
it is not a society like others.

00:12:26.504 --> 00:12:30.000
The Message it spreads, and because of 
 which it exists, requires obedience of the ones

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:33.743
representing the institutions, as well as the 
 obedience of the ordinary members.

00:12:34.563 --> 00:12:37.998
Because of the immutability of the 
 Message, the institution that's in

00:12:37.998 --> 00:12:42.335
its service is obligated to accept 
 changes that the Message demands,

00:12:42.335 --> 00:12:44.335
and the institution can’t be at rest.

00:12:44.581 --> 00:12:48.098
Just like the Son of Man, the 
 Church has no place to lay its head.

00:12:48.262 --> 00:12:53.173
The Church in the eschatological tension: 
 “straining toward what is ahead”,

00:12:53.173 --> 00:12:56.392
 lives in a constant pilgrimage and is 
 constantly moving on the way without

00:12:56.392 --> 00:13:00.360
depriving the fundamental structures of 
 the right to determine and direct its course.

00:13:02.287 --> 00:13:07.116
Business people hire experts to closely 
 examine the organization's business and

00:13:07.116 --> 00:13:09.526
indicate technical or psychological errors

00:13:10.223 --> 00:13:12.346
that slow down or interfere with its work.

00:13:12.346 --> 00:13:16.191
Clearly, the comparison between the Church 
 and a business company isn't possible

00:13:16.191 --> 00:13:21.348
but some principles can be applied to any 
institution in which people work for a common goal.

00:13:21.848 --> 00:13:27.055
The acceptance of critical reconsideration is 
 a part of every human effort and it is ignored

00:13:27.055 --> 00:13:28.481
to your detriment.

00:13:29.096 --> 00:13:31.506
If only this document has been taken seriously.

00:13:31.670 --> 00:13:34.818
One of the fundamental errors 
 that the Church  does these days

00:13:34.818 --> 00:13:36.818
and the reason

00:13:36.818 --> 00:13:43.041
that this whole Movement is not greater 
 (it is based on a few people that truly accepted it)

00:13:43.041 --> 00:13:47.829
is the fact that it offers sacramentalization 
 without evangelization.

00:13:48.116 --> 00:13:51.387
People must be brought to the 
 encounter with living God firstly.

00:13:52.740 --> 00:13:54.740
Then they need to be brought to sacraments.

00:13:54.740 --> 00:13:59.832
Look at the fruits of the violent 
 sacramentalization without evangelization.

00:13:59.832 --> 00:14:05.686
The youths can't wait to get out of the 
 Church after the sacrament of Confirmation.

00:14:05.686 --> 00:14:07.942
What kind of fruit is that? Non-existing.

00:14:09.541 --> 00:14:13.796
If there was humility that cardinal Leo Suenens 
 talks about just like in business companies -

00:14:13.796 --> 00:14:16.616
where they sit down and analyse 
 what they are doing wrong,

00:14:16.616 --> 00:14:18.288
our fruits would be different.

00:14:18.288 --> 00:14:22.912
Here in this parish, we did things differently 
 and the ones here that came because of the

00:14:22.912 --> 00:14:25.937
sacrament of confirmation are proof

00:14:26.429 --> 00:14:29.495
that Jesus' method is correct. What did Jesus do?

00:14:29.741 --> 00:14:33.463
Firstly He healed, He showed 
 the people that God is alive

00:14:34.201 --> 00:14:36.570
and then He established the Eucharist.

00:14:36.857 --> 00:14:41.440
Three years of charismatic phenomena 
 and then the establishment of Eucharist.

00:14:47.672 --> 00:14:50.738
We have a confirmation for this in 
 the teaching of the Catholic Church.

00:14:50.738 --> 00:14:54.214
Catechism of the Catholic Church point 1072 states:

00:14:55.854 --> 00:14:59.207
"The sacred liturgy does not exhaust 
 the entire activity of the Church":

00:14:59.207 --> 00:15:02.601
it must be preceded by evangelization, 
 faith, and conversion.

00:15:02.847 --> 00:15:08.988
It can then produce its fruits in the lives of 
 the faithful: new life in the Spirit, involvement in the

00:15:08.988 --> 00:15:11.521
mission of the Church, and service to her unity.

00:15:12.054 --> 00:15:13.275
It says

00:15:13.275 --> 00:15:17.899
that evangelization, faith, and conversion 
 must precede the sacred liturgy.

00:15:20.441 --> 00:15:23.015
We chose that method here in Botinec, Zagreb.

00:15:23.015 --> 00:15:24.646
Do you know what happened?

00:15:24.646 --> 00:15:27.343
Everyone started loving the holy Mass.

00:15:27.343 --> 00:15:31.639
Those who have criticized that method 
 the most have empty churches.

00:15:33.639 --> 00:15:36.418
This is an encouragement 
 to all of us to reassess,

00:15:36.418 --> 00:15:40.345
to get back to our roots, as Jesus says: 
 "come back to the first Love"

00:15:40.345 --> 00:15:43.452
and to His method that was successful 
 because of twelve fishermen,

00:15:43.452 --> 00:15:45.739
the strongest organization in history was established,

00:15:46.477 --> 00:15:49.379
if we observe the Church as just an organization.

00:15:50.199 --> 00:15:52.199
That organization has survived to this day.

00:15:55.479 --> 00:16:00.677
I divided that renewal, that we from the spiritual 
 renewal are obligated to transmit to the world,

00:16:00.677 --> 00:16:02.677
into five points.

00:16:02.923 --> 00:16:07.171
There are probably more than five but as 
 I was praying, God had put this on my heart

00:16:07.171 --> 00:16:10.442
to share with you. I believe that these 
 are the most important for you now.

00:16:10.442 --> 00:16:15.353
The first renewal that must proceed 
 from the spiritual renewal is moral renewal.

00:16:15.353 --> 00:16:17.845
Firstly, the restoration of the moral law.

00:16:18.091 --> 00:16:22.018
The moral law is necessary 
 and it won't be achieved

00:16:23.248 --> 00:16:26.273
without an encounter with living God.

00:16:26.273 --> 00:16:31.061
How many times did people try to 
 enforce some laws by force?

00:16:31.430 --> 00:16:35.111
How many times did they try to 
 make their children

00:16:35.111 --> 00:16:39.489
do something they didn't want to by force

00:16:39.489 --> 00:16:45.712
or try to make people in their companies and 
 communities do what they want by force,

00:16:45.712 --> 00:16:49.598
without relying on the Holy Spirit. 
 We can see what their results are.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:52.000
What people do out of fear,

00:16:52.492 --> 00:16:55.968
they won't do permanently but 
 only while the fear lasts.

00:16:56.255 --> 00:16:58.993
What people do out of love, from the internal

00:16:58.993 --> 00:17:00.000
encouragement,

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:03.148
 they will do permanently and they will be willing

00:17:03.148 --> 00:17:04.943
to invest their lives in it.

00:17:07.371 --> 00:17:12.692
I used a lot of texts from Pope Leo XII in this lecture.

00:17:12.692 --> 00:17:14.733
He was the first who spoke in this way.

00:17:14.733 --> 00:17:17.102
He opened the Church to the world 
 and restored its reputation.

00:17:17.635 --> 00:17:25.170
His mission was to bring Christianity closer 
 to the contemporary currents without giving up

00:17:25.170 --> 00:17:27.498
Christian principles.

00:17:29.179 --> 00:17:30.646
He wrote the following:

00:17:36.222 --> 00:17:41.164
"Religion is a wellspring of prosperity and 
 greatness for one nation and the main foundation

00:17:41.164 --> 00:17:42.590
of a well-ordered society.

00:17:42.590 --> 00:17:43.688
Indeed,

00:17:43.688 --> 00:17:48.189
when the religious feeling that 
 uplifts, ennobles the soul,

00:17:48.189 --> 00:17:51.296
and instils in it the principles 
 of justice and honesty weakens,

00:17:51.747 --> 00:17:56.002
one begins to fall and indulge in wild instincts

00:17:56.166 --> 00:17:59.519
and the sole pursuit of material interests.

00:17:59.519 --> 00:18:03.241
From there, as a logical consequence, hostilities,

00:18:03.241 --> 00:18:08.152
disagreements, corrupt conflicts, 
 and disorder of good order come.

00:18:08.152 --> 00:18:09.406
All this

00:18:09.406 --> 00:18:13.637
cannot successfully and completely repair 
 neither the rigor of the law nor the penalties of

00:18:13.637 --> 00:18:18.015
the courts nor the use of armed force itself."

00:18:21.992 --> 00:18:28.584
The pope clearly says that we can't expect 
 the moral renewal to happen without or with just

00:18:28.584 --> 00:18:35.545
a superficial religion but with one that truly 
 guides us to the encounter with living God.

00:18:37.308 --> 00:18:41.973
Even one of the greatest critiques of the Church 
 and one of the ideologists of the French Revolution,

00:18:41.973 --> 00:18:43.727
Francois Voltaire,

00:18:43.727 --> 00:18:50.000
realized that true order can emerge 
 only from the awe of God.

00:18:54.172 --> 00:18:58.427
He said his famous sentence: "If God did not 
 exist, it would be necessary to invent him."

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:00.960
When they asked him why

00:19:01.124 --> 00:19:04.477
he answered: "Just because it would maintain the order."

00:19:05.092 --> 00:19:08.855
This has been said by one of the greatest 
 ideologists of the French revolution

00:19:08.855 --> 00:19:14.135
even though he opposed the Church and the 
 position of the clergy:"If God did not exist, it would be

00:19:14.135 --> 00:19:15.889
necessary to invent him.“

00:19:21.178 --> 00:19:26.007
True moral change can come only from 
 the experience of meeting the living God.

00:19:27.032 --> 00:19:31.287
I decided not to commit some sins, for 
 example: that I will live premarital purity, that

00:19:31.287 --> 00:19:35.788
 I will give up some vices, just after 
 I met Jesus Christ as a person.

00:19:35.788 --> 00:19:37.829
That encounter is moving.

00:19:37.829 --> 00:19:45.691
People these days often portray God as lukewarmly. 
 He is Love, you're allowed to do anything...

00:19:45.691 --> 00:19:49.085
But not exactly! Every encounter 
 with living God is shocking.

00:19:49.782 --> 00:19:56.119
I had the opportunity of meeting the seers 
 from Medjugorje and the seer Ivan that he had

00:19:56.119 --> 00:20:00.825
only ten years when our Lady appeared to him 
 said that he spent that night under his bed

00:20:00.825 --> 00:20:02.825
because he was scared the Lady will come again.

00:20:02.825 --> 00:20:05.973
He said it was nice, full of love, but it was also scary.

00:20:06.424 --> 00:20:11.704
When Jacob had his first mystical experience 
 with God he said: "How terrifying is this place."

00:20:14.164 --> 00:20:17.804
That encounter shakes us from within. 
 If we have a sense of sacredness,

00:20:18.378 --> 00:20:23.002
that sense will encourage the 
 other moral virtues in us.

00:20:24.273 --> 00:20:29.512
One song says: “something is holy if 
 you tremble in front of it and admire it.”

00:20:29.512 --> 00:20:33.562
If you develop that sense, you'll change easily.

00:20:34.095 --> 00:20:37.120
Who knows who the author of this song is?

00:20:37.120 --> 00:20:40.801
I have heard it on the local radio the other day.

00:20:40.801 --> 00:20:44.523
Who would have said you can 
 find something useful there.

00:20:46.040 --> 00:20:47.630
That is the only way

00:20:48.245 --> 00:20:51.844
a true moral renewal can occur.

00:20:53.361 --> 00:20:56.837
Jesus said to the St. Faustina Kowalska 
 in her diary, paragraph 699:

00:20:56.837 --> 00:20:59.575
"Mankind will not have peace

00:20:59.575 --> 00:21:04.527
until it turns to the Fount of My Mercy."

00:21:07.274 --> 00:21:11.037
A return to the Lord is the only way

00:21:11.816 --> 00:21:15.702
to achieve moral and every other renewal.

00:21:15.702 --> 00:21:21.720
Every attempt to unite people and 
 peoples without God will fail.

00:21:21.720 --> 00:21:25.196
The first such attempt is 
 known in the tower of Babel

00:21:26.057 --> 00:21:28.262
in the book of Genesis 5.

00:21:29.287 --> 00:21:32.968
People gathered without God and started to 
 build a tower that will reach the heavens.

00:21:32.968 --> 00:21:34.968
Do you know what happened? 
 God confused their language.

00:21:35.460 --> 00:21:39.592
God will confuse the language of every such attempt.

00:21:39.592 --> 00:21:43.027
Look at the League of Nations, look at the 
 European Union and how it is falling apart,

00:21:43.027 --> 00:21:47.569
and look at Yugoslavia. All those attempts had failed.

00:21:47.569 --> 00:21:50.553
Look at the Church. It has remained for 2000 years

00:21:56.006 --> 00:21:59.236
because it is built on the foundations and the truth.

00:21:59.769 --> 00:22:01.605
The truth isn't an ideology.

00:22:02.425 --> 00:22:03.974
The truth is a person.

00:22:05.974 --> 00:22:10.000
That is why Jesus said: "I am the 
 way and the truth and the life.”

00:22:10.533 --> 00:22:15.772
The questions of what is the truth, which 
 option and ideology are true are superfluous.

00:22:17.002 --> 00:22:19.494
In the Hebrew way of thinking,

00:22:20.806 --> 00:22:27.316
everything that is true possesses endurance, 
 persistence, and the future.

00:22:27.316 --> 00:22:32.104
One of the greatest theologians of the 
 20th century, Cardinal Walter Kasper, says

00:22:32.104 --> 00:22:35.006
in his book Evangelium und Dogma the following:

00:22:35.006 --> 00:22:39.302
"The truth is always revealed 
 and manifested over time."

00:22:39.712 --> 00:22:43.721
Everything that is true possesses 
 endurance, persistence, and the future.

00:22:44.090 --> 00:22:47.074
So it takes time for the truth to reveal itself.

00:22:47.074 --> 00:22:49.566
That's why the Church has survived.

00:22:50.304 --> 00:22:53.288
Not because it is holy, trust me, there are 
 often cases when it's worse in the Church than

00:22:53.288 --> 00:22:55.756
in the world. I am familiar with 
 those structures so I know.

00:22:55.756 --> 00:22:58.119
But because it is of Divine origin

00:22:58.611 --> 00:23:00.915
and that origin is Jesus Christ.

00:23:09.074 --> 00:23:14.846
When somebody experiences God's 
 love it is not hard for him to keep order.

00:23:14.846 --> 00:23:17.133
When we started working with the youths here

00:23:17.133 --> 00:23:22.372
the school director told me that some of 
 them are the most undisciplined ones

00:23:22.372 --> 00:23:26.258
in the whole school and that he has 
 to call their parents almost every day.

00:23:27.283 --> 00:23:29.078
Do you know what is happening now?

00:23:30.431 --> 00:23:34.785
Each one of them has a programme. 
 It is a prayer programme that often includes

00:23:34.785 --> 00:23:37.892
up to 2 hours of prayer, training, and studying.

00:23:37.892 --> 00:23:41.983
When their programme expires they 
 come to us and ask for a new one.

00:23:41.983 --> 00:23:43.983
They want to be disciplined

00:23:43.983 --> 00:23:45.983
because they want growth.

00:23:46.147 --> 00:23:50.000
In psychology, we see that the 
 fundamental longing of a soul is for order.

00:23:52.583 --> 00:23:57.226
The moral renewal won't be a problem when 
 that authentic encounter with God happens,

00:23:57.226 --> 00:23:59.494
when you experience God's, authentic love.

00:23:59.494 --> 00:24:00.961
The second renewal,

00:24:01.535 --> 00:24:06.815
preceded by moral renewal, 
 is the renewal of the family.

00:24:06.815 --> 00:24:09.717
Family is the most attacked these days.

00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:13.189
If we look at the prophetic signs, 
 sister Lucia from Fatima

00:24:14.214 --> 00:24:18.797
warns us that humanity's last battle 
 will be a battle for the family.

00:24:18.797 --> 00:24:22.568
From the movements in the world

00:24:22.568 --> 00:24:28.546
through gender revolution, the violent 
 imposition of the Istanbul Convention,

00:24:28.546 --> 00:24:31.776
and so on, we can see that that battle already began.

00:24:31.776 --> 00:24:34.391
I'm asking you to have a prophetic view.

00:24:34.760 --> 00:24:37.006
We need to fight against that

00:24:39.343 --> 00:24:42.860
and be aware that we have 
 enough weapons for that fight.

00:24:42.860 --> 00:24:48.099
How many times did a few people beat a 
 kingdom or overthrow the empire just by

00:24:48.099 --> 00:24:50.796
firmly relying on God?

00:24:53.584 --> 00:24:57.265
Look at the Battle of Vienna, Battle of Lepanto.
 Look at the phenomenon related to our

00:24:57.265 --> 00:24:59.265
Lady of Sinj (Croatia).

00:24:59.265 --> 00:25:04.791
Our Lady of Fatima would not announce 
 that if we couldn't rely on her.

00:25:04.791 --> 00:25:10.000
We can see what does Our Lady has 
 to say to families today in some of her revelations.

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:15.034
I'll use a text from Our Lady's 
 message to Stefano Gobbi.

00:25:15.034 --> 00:25:18.773
And that's why I encourage all of 
 you, especially the ones who are parents

00:25:19.019 --> 00:25:23.922
or are planning to become ones, to rely on Mary.

00:25:25.029 --> 00:25:28.177
Our families will survive if we commit them to Mary.

00:25:28.792 --> 00:25:31.735
Blessed Cardinal Stepinac declared that

00:25:31.735 --> 00:25:36.154
love would return to the families 
 if the prayer of rosary returned.

00:25:36.605 --> 00:25:41.188
Saint Mother Teresa whose statue 
we have here and who preached here

00:25:41.188 --> 00:25:45.361
at this pulpit said: "Family that 
 prays together stays together."

00:25:46.222 --> 00:25:50.000
We will see what Our Lady says 
 to the  families that commit to her:

00:25:51.707 --> 00:25:57.192
"I am comforted by this day that has 
 passed in prayer and simple and cordial

00:25:57.192 --> 00:26:00.832
unity with this family that is dedicated 
 to me and belongs to me.

00:26:02.144 --> 00:26:05.169
I love you and I am with you. I am speaking 
 to you and I am guiding you because

00:26:05.169 --> 00:26:07.169
you're the means of my mothers will.

00:26:07.169 --> 00:26:12.285
These days I gather families and take 
 them into the depths of my immaculate hearth

00:26:12.613 --> 00:26:16.663
where I offer them shelter, safety, 
 consolation, and defence.

00:26:17.114 --> 00:26:20.631
As I love to be called the Mother 
 and the Queen of my priests,

00:26:20.631 --> 00:26:24.845
I love to be called the Mother and 
 the Queen of families devoted to me.

00:26:25.255 --> 00:26:27.302
I watch over their lives,

00:26:27.302 --> 00:26:29.223
care about their concerns,

00:26:29.223 --> 00:26:33.506
I am interested in the spiritual and 
 material goods of all of its members.

00:26:34.121 --> 00:26:37.556
When you commit a family 
 to my immaculate hearth

00:26:37.556 --> 00:26:41.448
it is the same as if you opened the door 
 of your home to Heavenly mother.

00:26:41.448 --> 00:26:43.612
You are asking her to come 
 in and you are giving her

00:26:43.612 --> 00:26:47.498
space so she could perform 
 her maternal duty even more.

00:26:48.810 --> 00:26:51.712
Where I enter, the sin comes out.

00:26:52.696 --> 00:26:57.074
Where I reside, Divine mercy 
 and light are always present.

00:26:57.074 --> 00:27:00.000
Where I live, purity, and holiness live

00:27:00.632 --> 00:27:05.584
and since the sacrament of marriage 
 gives you the special grace to grow together,

00:27:05.584 --> 00:27:08.814
I have to strengthen the unity of a family,

00:27:08.814 --> 00:27:12.536
bring husband and wife to 
 deeper spiritual communion

00:27:12.536 --> 00:27:17.939
and perfect their worldly love, 
 and put in Jesus's heart.

00:27:17.939 --> 00:27:20.431
I am constantly strengthening family unity and

00:27:20.431 --> 00:27:23.333
leading all of its members to greater understanding.

00:27:23.333 --> 00:27:27.998
I am giving new senses for needs, for 
 even stronger, stronger, and deeper unity."

00:27:31.278 --> 00:27:36.304
That is the strength we have to rely on. 
 If we want a renewal of families it has to

00:27:36.304 --> 00:27:38.485
happen throughout the prayer.

00:27:38.485 --> 00:27:42.166
There are many examples where a 
 husband and his wife had completely

00:27:42.166 --> 00:27:47.856
unsolvable situations, they couldn't even 
 talk for a second without fighting

00:27:49.086 --> 00:27:52.767
and we would just encourage 
 them to pray the rosary.

00:27:53.300 --> 00:27:57.719
Some amazing testimonies came out of that. 
 I experienced it myself in my family.

00:27:57.719 --> 00:28:00.785
There were a lot of quarrels before, 
 you'd say we were just like a normal family.

00:28:00.785 --> 00:28:03.523
My sister Lucija is also here, 
 she'd say everything is fine.

00:28:04.876 --> 00:28:07.081
But a family must have the 
 same atmosphere as a nest.

00:28:07.081 --> 00:28:10.000
I remember that when I was coming 
 back from school I'd rather go to

00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:12.410
some kind of a cafe and stay 
 there than come home.

00:28:13.148 --> 00:28:17.649
Arguments, intolerance, lack of love... 
 I remember the feeling I had when we started

00:28:17.649 --> 00:28:21.822
to pray the rosary again. I was 
 feeling happy  to come back home.

00:28:21.822 --> 00:28:22.961
I thought

00:28:22.961 --> 00:28:24.551
I'd never feel that.

00:28:25.863 --> 00:28:27.043
Why that happened?

00:28:27.043 --> 00:28:31.216
The prayer of the rosary brings us back 
 the love, unity, and it strengthens the relations.

00:28:34.537 --> 00:28:37.357
Likewise, I encourage all of you that still 
 haven't done The Nine Fridays Devotion to start today.

00:28:37.357 --> 00:28:39.098
Today is the first Friday this month.

00:28:39.098 --> 00:28:41.098
Use this mercy of Jesus's Heart.

00:28:41.098 --> 00:28:47.444
Jesus promised to St Margaret Mary Alacoque: 
 "I will establish peace in their families."

00:28:48.551 --> 00:28:54.856
I encourage the ones that began 
 with this Devotion to persist.

00:28:57.849 --> 00:29:02.227
The third renewal that is very 
 important and is in a crisis these days

00:29:02.227 --> 00:29:04.678
is the renewal of the national feeling.

00:29:04.842 --> 00:29:07.580
We must be proud

00:29:07.580 --> 00:29:10.000
for being Croats and we must be patriots.

00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:12.000
That doesn't mean that we impair

00:29:12.533 --> 00:29:15.189
the value of other nations. 
 Jesus was a patriot.

00:29:15.189 --> 00:29:17.189
He wept over Jerusalem.

00:29:18.542 --> 00:29:23.658
St. Paul, as a Jew who preached to 
 Gentiles, went that far that he said:

00:29:23.658 --> 00:29:27.708
“I'd burn in hell just for my 
 people of Israel to convert.”

00:29:29.708 --> 00:29:34.915
The truth is that the Jews are the 
 greatest patriots and they have no

00:29:34.915 --> 00:29:38.227
equal but that statement from a man like Paul,

00:29:38.227 --> 00:29:40.678
who knows pretty well what does burning in hell mean...

00:29:41.375 --> 00:29:46.983
He said I would burn in hell just 
 for my people of Israel to convert

00:29:46.983 --> 00:29:49.434
and realize that Jesus Christ is the Messiah.

00:29:50.541 --> 00:29:54.919
Saints give us an example that 
 we have to have that healthy patriotism.

00:29:55.370 --> 00:29:58.606
It is obvious that the new world order 
 wants to destroy that through the

00:29:58.606 --> 00:30:00.000
process of globalization.

00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:04.378
Globalization leads to the state 
 where everything comes down to one.

00:30:05.977 --> 00:30:07.813
One language,

00:30:07.813 --> 00:30:09.813
one culture,

00:30:10.205 --> 00:30:13.230
one type of music, even one type of food.

00:30:14.214 --> 00:30:17.198
When I was in Lisbon recently

00:30:17.649 --> 00:30:21.084
with my girlfriend we were 
 searching for a place

00:30:21.084 --> 00:30:24.724
to hear Fado and eat some Portuguese 
 food because we were in Portugal.

00:30:24.724 --> 00:30:27.462
We ended up in the Hard Rock 
 Cafe and McDonald’s.

00:30:28.200 --> 00:30:30.979
That has been done. They 
 want to destroy that feeling.

00:30:30.979 --> 00:30:35.357
Why? Because when you eradicate 
 someone and steal his identity,

00:30:35.357 --> 00:30:37.972
when he doesn't know where he is 
 heading and where he came from,

00:30:37.972 --> 00:30:40.136
one can easily be manipulated.

00:30:41.325 --> 00:30:42.587
And that's why

00:30:42.587 --> 00:30:43.931
we have to

00:30:43.931 --> 00:30:44.824
protect,

00:30:44.824 --> 00:30:46.578
jealously protect,

00:30:47.357 --> 00:30:49.357
our national identity.

00:30:50.997 --> 00:30:54.104
The Church always encourages 
 healthy nationalism.

00:30:54.104 --> 00:30:57.990
We need to differ healthy 
 and unhealthy nationalism.

00:30:58.564 --> 00:31:01.671
One of them is destructive, directed 
 towards the hate of someone

00:31:01.671 --> 00:31:03.753
and that one will never bring good fruits.

00:31:03.753 --> 00:31:06.573
A healthy nationalism is 
 directed towards creativity

00:31:07.147 --> 00:31:11.731
and a will to renew 
 and revive your nation,

00:31:12.264 --> 00:31:16.190
towards your wish to raise children 
 and give them to your nation so it survives,

00:31:17.297 --> 00:31:20.609
towards you staying here 
 and not moving abroad.

00:31:21.675 --> 00:31:24.823
Among us are some who 
 will one day testify

00:31:24.823 --> 00:31:27.479
that they chose to stay here

00:31:27.479 --> 00:31:30.914
and leave a better salary in Germany 
 thanks to the work of our community.

00:31:30.914 --> 00:31:35.620
I speak to them almost every day and, 
 believe me, none of them feel any regrets.

00:31:40.540 --> 00:31:43.852
Don't fall for that story. Open your eyes

00:31:46.066 --> 00:31:51.182
and get out of that pusillanimity. Pusillanimity 
 that we live in is almost like a demon.

00:31:51.592 --> 00:31:54.576
A demon needs to be evicted. We the 
 members of the deliverance ministry know

00:31:54.576 --> 00:31:56.740
that it is necessary to tear down his house too.

00:31:57.847 --> 00:32:01.528
The house that is established 
 on lies and bad news.

00:32:01.528 --> 00:32:04.102
This house convinced us that it's not 
 possible to succeed here on our territory.

00:32:04.102 --> 00:32:06.512
There are 200 of us in our community.

00:32:07.209 --> 00:32:10.316
We have youths in college, the ones 
 that finished college and are now

00:32:10.316 --> 00:32:12.579
working but no one is unemployed.

00:32:12.579 --> 00:32:15.153
Not a single one of us was 
 unemployed for more than a month.

00:32:16.793 --> 00:32:19.080
God won't abandon you.

00:32:21.367 --> 00:32:24.269
That's one more area that we need 
 to look at as prophets and open our eyes.

00:32:24.269 --> 00:32:26.802
We need to enter that healthy nationalism.

00:32:27.048 --> 00:32:31.180
Pope Pius XI says: "Unrestrained 
 nationalism is the fruit of the

00:32:31.180 --> 00:32:34.779
lust of the flesh, the lust of 
 the eyes, and the pride of life.

00:32:34.779 --> 00:32:38.009
We must distinguish healthy 
 and unhealthy nationalism.”

00:32:39.034 --> 00:32:42.797
I encourage you to do so. 
 How will you love your homeland?

00:32:42.797 --> 00:32:46.601
As deceased president, Kennedy says: 

00:32:47.216 --> 00:32:52.455
 "Ask not what your country can do 
 for you—ask what you can do for your country."

00:32:57.990 --> 00:32:59.293
This is an opportunity.

00:33:00.195 --> 00:33:03.876
If we look to the end 
 prophetically, biblically speaking

00:33:04.163 --> 00:33:06.737
emigration has always been a sign of a curse.

00:33:06.737 --> 00:33:09.270
Do you know who the first 
 wanderer on Earth was?

00:33:09.557 --> 00:33:10.696
Do you know?

00:33:12.172 --> 00:33:13.557
Cain, that is right.

00:33:13.557 --> 00:33:17.197
Cain was a murderer. Let's see what his curse was.

00:33:18.181 --> 00:33:23.953
After he killed his brother, God says this to Cain:

00:33:27.520 --> 00:33:32.513
"And the Lord said, "What have you done?
 Listen; your brother's blood

00:33:32.513 --> 00:33:34.718
is crying out to me from the ground!

00:33:35.415 --> 00:33:39.055
And now you are cursed from the ground, 
 which has opened its mouth to receive your

00:33:39.055 --> 00:33:41.195
brother's blood from your hand.

00:33:41.195 --> 00:33:44.835
When you till the ground, it will no 
 longer yield to you its strength;

00:33:44.835 --> 00:33:47.409
you will be a fugitive and 
 a wanderer on the earth."

00:33:48.311 --> 00:33:51.172
We can clearly see a biblical 
 and spiritual law that says:

00:33:51.172 --> 00:33:54.812
your brother's blood is crying out to me 
 from the ground and the repercussion:

00:33:54.812 --> 00:33:57.222
you will be a fugitive and 
 a wanderer on the earth.

00:33:58.288 --> 00:34:01.723
What we are obligated to do 
 as God's prophetical nation

00:34:01.723 --> 00:34:05.158
is to make the atonement and 
 repentance for a great amount of blood

00:34:05.527 --> 00:34:08.306
that is crying out from the ground for justice.

00:34:09.167 --> 00:34:11.167
That's why the descendants

00:34:11.618 --> 00:34:13.905
cannot be at peace and they wander.

00:34:13.905 --> 00:34:16.684
Leviticus says that

00:34:16.684 --> 00:34:20.980
when you rejected the Lord, 
 and gone after other gods,

00:34:20.980 --> 00:34:23.144
I will scatter thee among the heathen.

00:34:25.563 --> 00:34:28.260
What is happening to us is a sign of a curse.

00:34:29.818 --> 00:34:33.499
Material conditions are way 
 better than they were before.

00:34:34.155 --> 00:34:38.041
People nowadays fear to have more 
 children because they are scared

00:34:38.041 --> 00:34:40.205
they won't be able to afford them something.

00:34:40.738 --> 00:34:44.214
Take a look at how many 
 children our families had before

00:34:44.214 --> 00:34:48.838
fifty or seventy years although 
 they couldn't afford much.

00:34:48.838 --> 00:34:50.961
They literally had just bread and milk.

00:34:50.961 --> 00:34:52.961
Maybe an orange for Christmas.

00:34:52.961 --> 00:34:54.961
That's my grandfather's story.

00:34:57.339 --> 00:35:01.266
Open your eyes! I want you to rise 
 from this situation and understand

00:35:01.266 --> 00:35:03.184
the position we are in

00:35:03.184 --> 00:35:06.414
The solution to this emigration

00:35:06.414 --> 00:35:08.414
is in repentance

00:35:08.414 --> 00:35:10.414
for past events.

00:35:12.250 --> 00:35:16.423
As long as we don't remove that 
 spiritual barrier that's above us

00:35:16.423 --> 00:35:18.095
there will be no blessings.

00:35:18.300 --> 00:35:21.653
This church wasn't full up 
 until we removed that

00:35:21.653 --> 00:35:24.227
spiritual barrier here in Botinec, Zagreb.

00:35:24.227 --> 00:35:29.220
Whatever started here, it was going 
 for a month or two and fell silent.

00:35:30.655 --> 00:35:33.803
God will give a blessing. 
 He gave us the tools.

00:35:34.664 --> 00:35:39.657
That is a thing I want to teach you 
 through the upcoming year.

00:35:49.619 --> 00:35:53.382
I listed two more specific renewals

00:35:54.940 --> 00:35:58.211
that this renewal of national 
 feeling should lead to.

00:35:58.211 --> 00:36:00.744
The first one is the renewal of economics.

00:36:00.744 --> 00:36:04.425
God wants to bless his children 
 with material goods too.

00:36:04.425 --> 00:36:06.425
Here is the first lie

00:36:07.368 --> 00:36:09.368
that the devil tells us:

00:36:11.368 --> 00:36:15.213
God wants to deprive us of material goods.
 He is a tyrant. God wants us away from pleasure.

00:36:15.213 --> 00:36:17.213
That is not true!

00:36:17.213 --> 00:36:20.000
God created all the trees and 
 said eat from every tree

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:22.164
except this one in the middle.

00:36:22.451 --> 00:36:24.287
It was the tree of the 
 knowledge of good and evil.

00:36:24.287 --> 00:36:27.025
Meaning you decide for yourself 
 what is good and what is bad.

00:36:27.763 --> 00:36:32.059
The devil comes and says: “Did God say, 
 You shall not eat from any tree in the garden?”

00:36:35.052 --> 00:36:40.528
We need to differ the extremes. The extreme 
 of the prosperity, the gospel says that we

00:36:40.528 --> 00:36:45.439
must only carry out the commandments 
 of God if we want to be blessed.

00:36:45.439 --> 00:36:47.439
That is wrong. It is a heresy.

00:36:47.685 --> 00:36:49.685
And the other extreme

00:36:50.382 --> 00:36:53.325
that states that only poverty 
 can lead to holiness.

00:36:53.325 --> 00:36:55.038
Also not true!

00:36:55.489 --> 00:36:58.391
God wants to bless his nation. 
 God is a Father.

00:36:58.391 --> 00:37:03.261
Which father would not want 
 his children to have material goods

00:37:03.261 --> 00:37:05.794
if he knew it would not ruin them?

00:37:05.794 --> 00:37:10.295
He will deny them something only 
 when he knows it is leading them to perdition.

00:37:10.295 --> 00:37:12.828
Why do we think we are better than God?

00:37:13.607 --> 00:37:17.456
Didn't Jesus say: "If you then, though 
 you are evil, know how to give good gifts

00:37:17.456 --> 00:37:21.101
to your children, how much more 
 will your Father in heaven give..."

00:37:22.700 --> 00:37:26.053
When I read the extension 
 of Our Lady's message

00:37:26.053 --> 00:37:29.324
I wasn't sure is that Our Lady 
 or Benny Hinn speaking.

00:37:30.718 --> 00:37:34.153
It is not that funny for those of you 
 who don't know who Benny Hinn is.

00:37:34.932 --> 00:37:39.187
He is one of the most famous preachers 
 of the prosperity gospel, who has a private

00:37:39.187 --> 00:37:44.057
plane and has caused many scandals.

00:37:44.631 --> 00:37:46.262
Our Lady says:

00:37:46.843 --> 00:37:51.303
"I stand up for the material goods 
 of families that are dedicated to me.

00:37:51.303 --> 00:37:54.410
Children are the most 
 precious good of a family.

00:37:54.410 --> 00:37:57.435
Children are a sign of Jesus's 
 and my special love.

00:37:58.706 --> 00:38:03.699
I take special care of your job as well.
 I never leave you without God's providence.

00:38:03.699 --> 00:38:08.692
I take and open your hands to God's 
 plan that He accomplishes every day

00:38:08.692 --> 00:38:10.692
with the help of your cooperation.

00:38:10.692 --> 00:38:15.152
Just like my humble, faithful, and 
 daily maternal action in a little,

00:38:15.152 --> 00:38:20.473
poor Nazareth cottage made it 
 possible for the God’s plan, which

00:38:20.473 --> 00:38:23.662
was realized in the human growth 
 of my son Jesus who was called to

00:38:23.662 --> 00:38:26.769
execute the work of a redeemer 
 and your salvation, to fulfil.

00:38:26.769 --> 00:38:30.819
That's how I call you to follow 
 the Fathers' plan that is achieved

00:38:30.819 --> 00:38:34.254
with help of your human 
 collaboration and daily work.

00:38:34.254 --> 00:38:36.254
You have to do your part

00:38:37.115 --> 00:38:40.000
just like heavenly Father does his.“

00:38:42.164 --> 00:38:47.895
If you look closely, spiritual renewal 
 always preceded material renewal.

00:38:47.895 --> 00:38:50.000
Just look at Bosnia and Herzegovina.

00:38:50.000 --> 00:38:54.009
Take a look at the two places where 
 authentic spiritual renewal took place:

00:38:54.009 --> 00:38:56.583
the parish Surkovac and the parish Medjugorje.

00:38:57.526 --> 00:38:59.385
Look at how do people live there now.

00:38:59.385 --> 00:39:03.375
At the moment when Fra Ivo Pavic 
 came to Surkovac, he came from

00:39:03.375 --> 00:39:06.961
a doctorate in Gregorian in Rome.

00:39:06.961 --> 00:39:11.831
He came to a parish with barely a few 
 dozen Catholics and a destroyed church.

00:39:11.831 --> 00:39:15.635
God spoke to Fra Ivo, gave him a vision 
 that there will a source of living water be.

00:39:15.635 --> 00:39:19.836
These days, there are 20 to 50 
 busses on the weekends.

00:39:21.312 --> 00:39:23.025
He built a stadium.

00:39:23.025 --> 00:39:27.116
All the children from the parish go 
 to Zagreb for education and come

00:39:27.116 --> 00:39:28.501
back to Surkovac.

00:39:28.501 --> 00:39:32.797
Out of nowhere... That man baptizes 
 at least ten Muslims every Easter because

00:39:32.797 --> 00:39:34.961
they see that God is alive.

00:39:34.961 --> 00:39:37.166
That is a resource that you have in your hands.

00:39:37.166 --> 00:39:39.166
Just look at Medjugorje.

00:39:39.166 --> 00:39:43.790
There were three hundred tobacco 
 and vineyard growers, Herzegovinians there.

00:39:43.790 --> 00:39:45.790
I mean, the Herzegovinians 
 know their business but...

00:39:50.462 --> 00:39:55.291
What came from that? We were at the
 Medjugorje Youth Festival not too long ago.

00:39:55.291 --> 00:39:58.193
More than 70 000 young people were there.

00:39:58.193 --> 00:40:00.931
You can see all the different 
 flags of the world there.

00:40:00.931 --> 00:40:03.136
That renewal happened in 
 less than 40 years.

00:40:03.136 --> 00:40:05.587
Whatever is started there, succeeds.

00:40:06.817 --> 00:40:10.211
The real spiritual renewal will 
 lead to that kind of well-being

00:40:10.211 --> 00:40:14.384
because God does not neglect his people 
 but He asks us to meet our conditions.

00:40:15.942 --> 00:40:20.279
That's why I encourage you that 
 are still young to be enterprising.

00:40:20.279 --> 00:40:23.964
When I was in Poland on a youth 
 formation with Marin, when we

00:40:23.964 --> 00:40:27.404
were jumping through the 
 Special Forces camp in Wroclaw,

00:40:27.404 --> 00:40:30.347
we saw a thing that 
 did not happen here.

00:40:32.347 --> 00:40:35.996
They used up every cent of European funds

00:40:36.816 --> 00:40:41.071
and renovated orchards and built 
 highways. Poland lives from that.

00:40:41.071 --> 00:40:42.907
Poland has a government

00:40:43.399 --> 00:40:47.490
such that the head of it recently declared 
 that his only goal is to harmonize the

00:40:47.490 --> 00:40:49.490
state's laws with God's law.

00:40:51.285 --> 00:40:56.196
I am calling you. Have the interest, be 
 enterprising, and overcome that discouragement.

00:40:58.451 --> 00:41:02.583
Especially now when you're finishing 
 college. Start thinking about that.

00:41:03.772 --> 00:41:07.043
The most important thing is for someone 
 to tell you that it really is possible.

00:41:07.043 --> 00:41:09.043
It is possible! 

00:41:10.560 --> 00:41:14.487
And you as Christians need to 
 be the ones who withdraw.

00:41:14.487 --> 00:41:16.692
Let us take a look at what 
 the Popes say.

00:41:16.692 --> 00:41:19.389
Pope Pius XI states:

00:41:20.537 --> 00:41:23.480
"The Church is a source of temporal prosperity.

00:41:33.320 --> 00:41:37.411
We thought, on the other hand, 
 that those who run the public affairs

00:41:37.411 --> 00:41:41.215
would search for original causes 
 of rebellion and fratricidal struggle

00:41:41.215 --> 00:41:44.568
and that they would recognize fatal 
 but natural fruit of the bad seed

00:41:44.568 --> 00:41:48.905
that was planted on the Italian peninsula 
 with impunity and for a long time."

00:41:51.242 --> 00:41:56.235
Furthermore, the Pope says: “Only the 
 principles of Christian social organization

00:41:56.235 --> 00:41:59.219
are the ones that renew nations and 
 they become the condition of their

00:41:59.219 --> 00:42:03.983
material prosperity." Let us look 
 at what Pope Leo XII says:

00:42:03.983 --> 00:42:08.253
"The Church is a source of temporal 
 prosperity. Although the Church as

00:42:08.253 --> 00:42:11.298
an immortal work of merciful God 
 strives for the salvation of souls and

00:42:11.298 --> 00:42:15.290
eternal happiness - it is in the 
 very realm of human things;

00:42:15.290 --> 00:42:17.905
by the time of such and so 
 many benefits, that it would

00:42:17.905 --> 00:42:21.668
not be able to obtain them 
 greater and more if it were

00:42:21.668 --> 00:42:24.939
constitutional chapters and 
 directly in order to guarantee

00:42:24.939 --> 00:42:26.652
the welfare of this life."

00:42:28.292 --> 00:42:31.563
In translation, he says that if we 
 were to remove the supernatural part,

00:42:31.563 --> 00:42:34.629
which is the most important, or 
 shortly, the salvation of souls,

00:42:34.629 --> 00:42:38.638
the effect of Church doctrine 
 on material prosperity would

00:42:38.638 --> 00:42:43.016
be sufficient to guarantee prosperity 
 in life and the irreplaceable role of

00:42:43.016 --> 00:42:44.893
Church in history.

00:42:46.984 --> 00:42:48.451
That

00:42:49.353 --> 00:42:52.255
is something we need 
 to become aware of.

00:42:52.460 --> 00:42:57.166
Our lifestyle here, in the 
 community, needs to spread out.

00:42:59.462 --> 00:43:02.897
We need to learn how to operate 
 following the law of God.

00:43:03.594 --> 00:43:09.038
In his book "Fighting Corruption and Sin", 
 Pope Francis says:

00:43:09.426 --> 00:43:15.321
"Sin is forgiven but corruption 
 cannot be forgiven. It must be cured.

00:43:15.321 --> 00:43:18.633
A corrupted man is not aware 
 of his condition and he becomes

00:43:18.633 --> 00:43:24.586
contagious for society. Corruption is a 
 cobweb that spreads by imposing complicity.

00:43:25.447 --> 00:43:28.718
A rotten hearth can no longer 
 see its sin, rather the hearth

00:43:28.718 --> 00:43:33.260
makes a lifestyle out of sin by elevating 
 it to a level of virtue or at least socially

00:43:33.260 --> 00:43:34.891
acceptable norms."

00:43:35.752 --> 00:43:39.433
That is the renewal I am talking about. 
 Christian entrepreneurs need to be

00:43:39.433 --> 00:43:42.991
the ones that will show that a 
 righteous way is possible.

00:43:44.795 --> 00:43:46.795
God gives his blessing to that.

00:43:46.795 --> 00:43:49.820
Trust me, I am saying this 
 from my own experience

00:43:49.820 --> 00:43:54.936
and the experiences of many friends 
 that dared to leave their business to God.

00:43:55.747 --> 00:44:00.248
The last renewal that needs to 
 happen but many run away from it...

00:44:01.027 --> 00:44:03.027
They say: "Politics is dirty.",

00:44:03.027 --> 00:44:05.864
"Politics is a...", there 
 are many expressions.

00:44:05.864 --> 00:44:10.488
 I have heard a good one lately: 
 "Politics is not electricity, but it kills."

00:44:13.481 --> 00:44:16.055
Christians are obliged to engage in politics.

00:44:16.055 --> 00:44:18.055
The fifth renewal is a political renewal.

00:44:18.055 --> 00:44:21.599
God created the world and since 
 then has been leading it in one

00:44:21.599 --> 00:44:24.238
specific way - through people.

00:44:24.238 --> 00:44:27.427
In the Bible, we can see that a change 
 always begins with the revelation

00:44:27.427 --> 00:44:32.912
of God to a man. Either to Abraham or 
 Moses or through Jesus who gets an

00:44:32.912 --> 00:44:34.912
anointing for a specific act.

00:44:36.625 --> 00:44:40.438
The Church is independent of any 
 party policy and does not aspire

00:44:40.438 --> 00:44:45.267
to political domination, but it has 
 a prophetic role. Therefore, the Church

00:44:45.267 --> 00:44:46.857
must warn

00:44:46.857 --> 00:44:51.317
whenever the passed laws are not in 
 accordance with or break the law of God.

00:44:51.317 --> 00:44:56.597
The Church must encourage the lay 
 believers to get actively involved

00:44:56.597 --> 00:45:01.549
in healthy political options 
 that foster Christian values.

00:45:02.000 --> 00:45:05.763
Maybe there are very few of these 
 options just because you are passive.

00:45:09.289 --> 00:45:13.339
God hates lukewarmness more than anything.

00:45:13.339 --> 00:45:18.168
In the book of Revelation we 
 spot such a harsh Jesus' charge:

00:45:18.168 --> 00:45:21.020
"I wish you were either one or the other! 
 So, because you are lukewarm—neither

00:45:21.020 --> 00:45:23.881
hot nor cold—I am about to 
 spit you out of my mouth."

00:45:23.881 --> 00:45:25.881
We can see that God is 
 disgusted by lukewarmness.

00:45:27.439 --> 00:45:30.833
That is why we need to become 
 aware of the responsibility we have

00:45:30.833 --> 00:45:34.596
and get involved in one way or 
 another. You can do it by voting.

00:45:34.596 --> 00:45:37.826
Start praying and be open and let 
 God show you where and in which

00:45:37.826 --> 00:45:39.826
way He is calling you.

00:45:40.810 --> 00:45:43.671
Take a look at what does blessed 
 Ivan Merz says about this topic:

00:45:54.577 --> 00:45:58.627
"It is a delusion to want to completely 
 separate religion from politics.

00:45:58.627 --> 00:46:02.349
Whoever claims that divine laws 
 apply only to private and not to

00:46:02.349 --> 00:46:06.686
public and state life and that the Church 
 must not interfere in political life

00:46:06.686 --> 00:46:09.506
falls under the condemnation of liberalism.

00:46:09.506 --> 00:46:12.408
Catholics have a duty to engage in politics.

00:46:12.408 --> 00:46:17.483
The faith commands Catholics to 
 participate in political and social life.

00:46:19.303 --> 00:46:23.845
Let Catholics take over public services 
 and participate in public affairs so that

00:46:23.845 --> 00:46:26.419
that they can be christianized." 

00:46:28.059 --> 00:46:31.084
We can see that Popes went that far

00:46:33.052 --> 00:46:36.528
and they said that Catholics 
 must enrol in political options

00:46:36.528 --> 00:46:40.537
even if they are not

00:46:41.029 --> 00:46:44.833
completely in accordance with 
 Church law so they can heal them.

00:46:44.997 --> 00:46:48.596
I've had an opportunity to talk to Columbian 
 missionary Marino Restrepo - one of the

00:46:48.596 --> 00:46:51.559
greatest prophets of our days.

00:46:51.867 --> 00:46:54.080
We talked about politics in particular

00:46:54.080 --> 00:46:57.327
and he brought up the 
 example of the prophet Daniel.

00:46:57.327 --> 00:47:02.648
Daniel was at the court of the pagan 
 kings' Nebuchadnezzar and Cyrus

00:47:02.648 --> 00:47:06.247
but he made a great number of good 
 decisions for the people of Israel there.

00:47:06.247 --> 00:47:08.575
If we want to wash our 
 hands of that responsibility

00:47:08.575 --> 00:47:11.149
by saying that some options are

00:47:11.149 --> 00:47:13.149
just too dirty,

00:47:13.149 --> 00:47:16.050
too far away from God's law, 
 that they are too repulsive,

00:47:16.050 --> 00:47:18.378
let's take a look at what 
 the Popes say about that.

00:47:21.043 --> 00:47:25.011
Pope Leo XIII says: 

00:47:25.011 --> 00:47:30.496
"Let Catholics participate in public 
 affairs even where legislation is ungodly.

00:47:30.496 --> 00:47:36.391
In defending the faith, Catholics must be 
 united in the political field, even if they are in

00:47:36.391 --> 00:47:38.391
more than one allowed party."

00:47:38.391 --> 00:47:41.334
The Pope encourages us to a certain cunning.

00:47:41.334 --> 00:47:46.491
Jesus himself said: "So be as shrewd 
 as snakes and harmless as doves.”

00:47:47.434 --> 00:47:50.000
I know it won't be easy, but 
 the Pope encourages us

00:47:50.000 --> 00:47:52.574
to take that responsibility as well.
 Even if everything is ungodly,

00:47:52.574 --> 00:47:54.943
take part in it and be as the prophet Daniel.

00:47:54.943 --> 00:47:57.845
The prophet Daniel was 
 as if inserted by God

00:47:57.845 --> 00:48:00.829
into all these authorities, and 
 in the end, with his prayer and

00:48:00.829 --> 00:48:05.781
advice, he led the people of Israel 
 to return from the Babylonian exile

00:48:05.781 --> 00:48:07.781
to the Promised Land.

00:48:09.175 --> 00:48:12.036
So we don't need to wait until 
 everything is perfect because it

00:48:12.036 --> 00:48:13.298
won't be perfect that soon.

00:48:13.298 --> 00:48:17.184
We need to be the ones that will heal.

00:48:19.234 --> 00:48:22.464
In the end, I will give you 
 an example of such a ruler

00:48:22.464 --> 00:48:25.366
a saint as a role model.

00:48:26.514 --> 00:48:29.539
So you can see that what 
 I'm talking about really is possible.

00:48:29.539 --> 00:48:32.400
There were such politicians in 
 the 20th century as well.

00:48:32.400 --> 00:48:36.532
Josip will talk about 
 Robert Schumman, but this

00:48:36.901 --> 00:48:38.901
is a role model...

00:48:39.762 --> 00:48:42.254
Does anyone know who this saint is?

00:48:44.058 --> 00:48:46.550
This is Saint Louis IX.

00:48:46.550 --> 00:48:51.707
He was a French canonized king 
 from the Kapetovic dynasty.

00:48:52.691 --> 00:48:56.331
He used to feed 120 poor people 
 in his court and he completely

00:48:56.331 --> 00:48:58.495
eradicated poverty from France.

00:48:59.069 --> 00:49:01.069
He advocated for that himself.

00:49:01.069 --> 00:49:05.693
He did not neglect schooling. He founded 
 the Sorbonne University that is one of the

00:49:05.693 --> 00:49:07.693
best universities nowadays.

00:49:08.800 --> 00:49:14.162
He was a man of deep faith, he regularly 
 prayed breviary, approached the sacraments,

00:49:14.162 --> 00:49:17.925
fasted often, performed strict penances. 
 France was experiencing the greatest

00:49:17.925 --> 00:49:21.114
material and spiritual 
 blessing during his reign.

00:49:22.508 --> 00:49:28.075
He was married to Margaret and it is 
 well known that they had a harmonious

00:49:28.075 --> 00:49:31.148
and gentle marriage. That is very 
 rare for the Middle Ages when

00:49:31.148 --> 00:49:33.066
marriage was often 
 seen as a necessary evil.

00:49:33.066 --> 00:49:35.148
They found each other, but the 
 wives could hardly wait for her

00:49:35.148 --> 00:49:37.845
husband to die so they can go to the 
 convent. That is what some married saints did.

00:49:37.845 --> 00:49:40.533
Here it states that Louis and Margaret had 
 had a harmonious marriage, gentle love,

00:49:40.533 --> 00:49:42.000
and eleven children.

00:49:42.000 --> 00:49:46.206
Louis blessed and prayed for each 
 of these children in the evening.

00:49:46.206 --> 00:49:50.789
Later on, I will play for you the will 
 that he wrote to his heir son.

00:49:51.240 --> 00:49:55.577
He died in the Crusades where 
 he answered the Pope's call.

00:49:56.110 --> 00:50:00.430
We can see an example of a true Christian 
 ruler and an example that it is possible.

00:50:00.430 --> 00:50:02.799
And such a ruler is a fruit of prayer.

00:50:02.799 --> 00:50:04.799
How did Moses come to Israel?

00:50:05.168 --> 00:50:09.467
Because people were crying. It is said, 
 "The cry of the Israelites ascended to the Lord,"

00:50:09.467 --> 00:50:12.000
and the fruit of that cry was the call of Moses.

00:50:12.246 --> 00:50:18.551
We too are invited to get involved and 
 pray for those in authority so God sends

00:50:18.551 --> 00:50:20.000
us such people.

00:50:21.435 --> 00:50:24.419
We can see the will that Louis writes to his son:

00:50:24.419 --> 00:50:28.650
"Dear son, first of all, I teach you to love 
 the Lord your God with all your

00:50:28.650 --> 00:50:30.642
heart and with all your strength.

00:50:30.642 --> 00:50:33.216
Without that, there is no salvation.

00:50:33.216 --> 00:50:37.840
May your heart be gentle when it comes 
 to the poor, the wretched, and the sad.

00:50:37.840 --> 00:50:41.398
Come to their aid according to 
 your abilities and comfort them.

00:50:41.398 --> 00:50:45.284
Be thankful to God for all the 
 good deeds he has given you

00:50:45.284 --> 00:50:48.104
and so you will be worthy 
 to receive even greater.

00:50:48.104 --> 00:50:53.138
Be righteous to your subjects,
 and keep the line of righteousness,

00:50:53.138 --> 00:50:54.957
and do not turn to the 
 right or to the left.

00:50:54.957 --> 00:50:57.736
Until you are sure where 
 the truth is, be more on

00:50:57.736 --> 00:51:00.474
the side of the poor than the rich.

00:51:00.474 --> 00:51:05.087
Take care that all your subjects 
 keep justice and peace."

00:51:06.923 --> 00:51:12.449
Imagine politicians writing such 
 messages to their successors nowadays.

00:51:13.351 --> 00:51:15.064
Where would we be...?

00:51:15.064 --> 00:51:17.064
What I want to tell you is:

00:51:18.335 --> 00:51:23.656
do not lose hope because Christ 
 is our head and we rely on him.

00:51:23.656 --> 00:51:26.953
We rely on Christ who is the living 
 God and who will never run out of

00:51:26.953 --> 00:51:28.871
strength and happiness.

00:51:28.871 --> 00:51:31.568
We are the members of His 
 body and He is the head.

00:51:31.568 --> 00:51:37.212
He constantly renews, revives, and 
 gives new strength to his Church.

00:51:37.212 --> 00:51:40.483
What you need to do is to believe.

00:51:40.483 --> 00:51:43.221
When the crowd pushed around Jesus,

00:51:44.615 --> 00:51:46.615
thousands pushed around him,

00:51:47.558 --> 00:51:49.558
one woman touched him with faith.

00:51:52.100 --> 00:51:54.100
He asked: "Who touched me?"

00:51:55.002 --> 00:51:57.945
Saint Peter rightly asked Jesus: "The 
 multitude throng thee and press thee,

00:51:57.945 --> 00:51:59.798
and sayest thou, who touched me?"

00:51:59.798 --> 00:52:02.577
Jesus replied: "Somebody hath 
 touched me." and He said

00:52:03.356 --> 00:52:06.791
that he perceived that because: 
 "virtue is gone out of me."

00:52:07.242 --> 00:52:10.759
If we truly believe in the Lord, 
 that power that is in Him will be

00:52:10.759 --> 00:52:14.481
released in us as well and 
 we will watch His miracles.

00:52:14.481 --> 00:52:19.556
He will heal your tiredness, 
 lukewarmth, hopelessness,

00:52:19.556 --> 00:52:22.130
disappointment and he will 
 give you the new strength.

00:52:22.130 --> 00:52:25.811
There wasn't a single young man when 
 we started operating in this parish.

00:52:25.811 --> 00:52:28.426
This Saturday we had the first 
 wedding in our community.

00:52:28.426 --> 00:52:32.886
Thank God, there were around 
 400 people but mostly youth.

00:52:32.886 --> 00:52:36.116
I remembered that back when we 
 started there wasn't a single one.

00:52:36.567 --> 00:52:41.517
I remembered that quote that Patriarch 
 Jacob said when he came before Pharaoh,

00:52:41.517 --> 00:52:45.157
he says: "I came here alone, and behold, 
 I have become a multitude of people."

00:52:46.387 --> 00:52:50.478
It is the living God who can do 
 this in your heart, in your family,

00:52:50.478 --> 00:52:54.569
in your parish and everywhere 
 you come to be the salt of the earth

00:52:54.569 --> 00:52:56.168
and the light of the world.

00:52:56.168 --> 00:52:57.480
Amen.

